    <item>
      <title>哈里伯顿认为网络攻击不太可能造成重大影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/halliburton-says-cyberattack-unlikely-to-have-material-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的水力压裂服务提供商哈里伯顿公司表示，最近发生的网络安全攻击虽然扰乱了其业务，但不太可能对其财务或运营产生重大影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/halliburton-says-cyberattack-unlikely-to-have-material-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能推动苹果股价上涨 有望迎来关键考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/apple-aapl-rally-fueled-by-ai-promises-approaches-a-crucial-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司即将推出的 iPhone 因承诺的人工智能功能而使其股价飙升。如果以历史经验为鉴，至少在短期内，这些涨幅似乎很脆弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/apple-aapl-rally-fueled-by-ai-promises-approaches-a-crucial-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:55:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
